<L>Time-<HI>Serving, Swerving</HI> still from God They <HI>Scatter.</HI></L>
<L>They <HI>Sooth,</HI> speak <HI>Smooth,</HI> Charm, Dawb, Sow Pillowes, <HI>Flatter,</HI></L>
