<P><HI>T.D. Another of thy Remarkable</HI> passages, in the first Narrative, is of one of our friends, who by a meer mistake, <HI>charged one of your Ministers,</HI> Peter Domsell, <HI>who was cleare, instead of another, who was guilty of it, as slandering me falsely with taking pay from the Pope.</HI></P>
