<P>And whereas our <HI>unjust Iusticiaries</HI> strike hard against us, as they think, with that <HI>True Story Rom.</HI> 9. of <HI>Iacob</HI> and <HI>Esau</HI>'s being the <HI>one loved, th<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> other <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 span"> yet, being <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word">, <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">me neither good nor evil.</HI></P>
<P><HI>Rep.</HI> 1. I say, and so would they too, if they could once sea that <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word">
