<P>And now whereas <HI>T.D.</HI> and those <HI>Divines</HI> from whom he must come to be <HI>divided,</HI> before ever he know his part in the <HI>undivided Christ,</HI> do (<HI>uno ore</HI>) confesse so far unto this truth as to tell it further, then they are a|ware,
