<L>Exeo, cum multis aliis, ex. Orbe, ut in Orbe</L>
<L><HI>Piscator Ictus, Laesus,</HI> Amicusei,</L>
<L><HI>Piscilegens</HI> quoscunque <HI>bonos</HI> in vasa, at in ipsum</L>
<L><HI>Infernum</HI> abjiciens triste, malum que <HI>malos.</HI></L>
<L>Tupetis Exitium, Tibimet petis ipse Ruinam,</L>
